                <note rend="inline" type="source">Marshall Mission Files, Lot 54–D270:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Colonel <persName type="from">Marshall S. Carter</persName> to
                        General <persName type="to">Marshall</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-01-05">5 January
                            1947</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>89012. Reur 1907. The President stated his complete agreement to your views
                    expressed in reference message. The White House press release will be made at
                    1900 Monday 6 January Eastern Standard Time for use of radio that night and for
                    morning papers Tuesday 7 January.</p>
            </div>
